@node "latex" "LaTex and BiBTeX"
LaTeX is a document preparation system that is used to create documents,
articles, technical reports etc.

BiBTeX creates from a list of references a bibliography file ready made for
LaTeX in different styles.

BibCard is a program to maintain the reference list in a friendly manner.

@endnode

